1. *Ptice* leti preko pustinje. (The birds are flying over the desert.)
2. Oni vole da čuju *ptice* pevanje. (They love to hear the birds singing.) 
3. Dete je napravilo kućicu za *ptice*. (The child made a house for the birds.)
4. *Ptice* leti sa severa na jug. (The birds are flying from north to south.)
5. Na prozoru je bilo mnogo *ptica*. (There were many birds on the window.)